{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">验证力的合成的平行四边形定则。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此实验是要用互成角度的两个力与一个力产生相同的效果（即：使橡皮条在某一方向伸长一定的长度），看其用平行四边形定则求出的合力与这一个力是否在实验误差允许范围内相等，如果在实验误差允许范围内相等，就验证了力的平行四边形定则。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">木板、白纸、橡皮条、弹簧测力计</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用两个弹簧秤共同拉动小圆环，使橡皮条伸长，结点到达某一位置</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">O</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．用铅笔描下结点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">O</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的位置和两个拉力方向，并记录弹簧秤的读数。在白纸上按比例作出两个弹簧秤的拉力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">F</span></span></span><sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1</span></span></sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span>F</span></span><sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></span></sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的图示，根椐平行四边形定则求出合力</span>F<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．只用一个弹簧秤，把橡皮条的结点拉到与前面相同的位置</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">O</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，记下弹簧秤的读数和方向。按同样的比例</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">做出这个弹簧秤的拉力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">F</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&#39;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的图示。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．比较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">F</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&#39;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与用平行四边形定则求得的合力</span>F<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在实验误差允许的范围内是否相等。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．改变两个分力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">F</span></span></span><sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1</span></span></sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span>F</span></span><sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></span></sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的大小和夹角。再重复实验两次，比较每次的</span>F<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">F</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&#39;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否在实验误差允许的范围内相等。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">互成角度的两个力的合成满足力的平行四边形定则。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．用弹簧秤测拉力时，应使拉力沿弹簧秤的轴线方向，橡皮条、弹簧秤应位于与纸面平行的同一平面内。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．同一次实验中，橡皮条拉长后的结点位置</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">O</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">必须保持不变。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}